{
  "texts": [
    "In their simplest form, these methods often apply pre-trained CNN models, e.g., AlexNet, VGG, GoogLeNet, etc., on various image datasets.",
    "In what follows, each category of Fig. 13 is examined separately.",
    "Semantic segmentation-projection-based methodsIn projection-based methods, point clouds are projected into 2D images.",
    "These methods are efficient in terms of computational complexity and can result in improvement of performance for various 3D tasks by capturing several views of the area of interest.",
    "Predictions are then made based on the outputs, either through fusion or majority voting."
  ]
}